Source.Name: dia
Source.Description: Dia Diagram Editor is free Open Source drawing software. Dia supports more than 30 different diagram types like flowcharts, network diagrams, database models. More than a thousand readymade objects help to draw professional diagrams. Dia can read and write a number of different raster and vector image formats.
